title: Now hiring: Durango Wood Fire Grill, A-B Tech, more
text:
1. Bartenders, servers, hosts, busser, cooks : Durango Wood Fire Grill is now hiring for all hourly positions including bartenders, servers, hosts, busser and cooks. [ Apply today ]
2. Outside sales : Atlanta Windustrial in Lithonia has an opening for experienced outside sales. Experience in the pipe valves and fittings business is a plus. [ Apply today ]
3. Landscape architect : Two - five years of design and build residential experience preferred. [ Apply today ]
4. CDL A drivers : Stewart Stainless Supply Inc.â€‹ seeks local and road drivers. CDL A and two years driving experience required. [ Apply today ]
5. Software test engineer : Vision3 Solutions, Inc. in Suwanee is seeking an engineer to develop, design, plan and test user interface and middleware for video technology products in Linux/Windows environment. [ Apply today ]
6. Foreman : Knight Construction is seeking an experienced and dependable foremen with a minimum of three years commercial drywall experience, and knowledge of metal stud framing, finishing and acoustical ceilings. [ Apply today ]
7. Machinist : Alum-A-Lift, Inc. seeks an experienced machinist with knowledge of machining processes, manual mill and lathe. [ Apply today ]
8. Vice president for business and finance/CFO : A-B Tech seeks a VP/CFO who will be responsible for overall supervision of the business services and all financial operations of the college. [ Apply today ]
9. Sterile processing tech : SOSI is seeking a technician that is very dependable, extremely focused and detail oriented. [ Apply today ]
